author = {Leo J. Donner and Bruce L. Wyman and Richard S. Hemler and Larry W. Horowitz and Yi Ming and Ming Zhao and Jean-Christophe Golaz and Paul Ginoux and S.-J. Lin and M. Daniel Schwarzkopf and John Austin and Ghassan Alaka and William F. Cooke and Thomas L. Delworth and Stuart M. Freidenreich and C. T. Gordon and Stephen M. Griffies and Isaac M. Held and William J. Hurlin and Stephen A. Klein and Thomas R. Knutson and Amy R. Langenhorst and Hyun-Chul Lee and Yanluan Lin and Brian I. Magi and Sergey L. Malyshev and P. C. D. Milly and Vaishali Naik and Mary J. Nath and Robert Pincus and Jeffrey J. Ploshay and V. Ramaswamy and Charles J. Seman and Elena Shevliakova and Joseph J. Sirutis and William F. Stern and Ronald J. Stouffer and R. John Wilson and Michael Winton and Andrew T. Wittenberg and Fanrong Zeng},
title = {The Dynamical Core, Physical Parameterizations, and Basic Simulation Characteristics of the Atmospheric Component {AM3} of the {GFDL} Global Coupled Model {CM3}},
